Ladies! I’m inviting you to join me at Copperwood Trail, as I host an exclusive and intimate Women’s Self-Care Retreat! I encourage you to step away from the busyness of your life and spend time in nature, reconnecting with yourself - mind, heart and soul. Many of you know me as a Radio Personality, but I am also a Reiki Master and Women’s Mentor, and as such, I have created a retreat that will include a mindful meditation, an open women’s circle, and a powerful, grounding session with horses, led by Certified EAL Facilitator, Gabriella Vamvakidis. You will leave the retreat feeling grounded, refreshed, lighter and uplifted!

Details:
Women’s Self-Care Retreat: Relax, Release and Renew
Thursday May 25, 2023
10AM-2PM
Copperwood Trail, Stouffville
Light refreshments will be served

DM to book your spot now! Space is limited.

#womensretreat #retreat #wellness #women #womenempowerment #womenempoweringwomen #womensupportingwomen #selfcare #selflove #horsehumanharmony #copperwoodtrail #stouffville #ontario #investinyourself

My Women’s Self-Care Retreat at @copperwoodtrail is ONE MONTH away! It is my hope that you will take this opportunity to focus on YOU. Together, we’ll RELAX and LET GO through meditation, RELEASE through an open discussion, and GROUND through a hands-on session with horses, led by Certified EAL Facilitator, Gabriella Vamvakidis. 

I invite you to share this experience with a special woman in your life: your mom, your sister, your bestie! 

Please note: this retreat is small, in order to allow for more open conversation and deeper connection, so reserve your spot(s) now!
